---
title: Protein-Packed Rice Bowl with Cashews, Sesame and Green Beans
description: Hearty brown rice, nuts, seeds, and veggies join forces for an energizing dinner of champions. Thanks to the addition of aromatics like soy sauce, ginger, and garlic, you’ll get a pop of umami flavor in every bite.
